Depends: docker-ce (>= 24.0.0) | docker.io (>= 24.0.0), docker-compose-plugin (>= 2.20.0)
Recommends: nvidia-docker2, curl
Maintainer: Your Organization <support@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/martinmanuel9/jitc_genai
Description: AI-powered research and verification system
 GenAI Research provides comprehensive AI-powered research and
 verification capabilities using advanced AI models. Features include:
 .
 - Multi-agent test plan generation with Actor-Critic system
 - RAG-enhanced document analysis with citation tracking
 - Test card creation with Word export
 - Support for cloud LLMs (OpenAI) and local models (Ollama)
 - US-based model compliance (Meta, Microsoft, Snowflake)
 - Complete on-premises deployment option
 .
 The system uses Docker Compose for orchestration and includes FastAPI backend,
 Streamlit web UI, PostgreSQL database, ChromaDB vector store, Redis cache,
 and Celery background worker.
